u2net.onnx — background-removal model
=====================================

This directory holds the u2net ONNX model used for background removal (rembg)
in image post-processing (outfit previews, world/map images). It is NOT used
for face swapping.

The model file (u2net.onnx, ~168 MB) is NOT committed to this repository — see
.gitignore (/models/). Download it with:

    ./scripts/fetch_models.sh

